backend_merchant:
This is some backend code that is used so the merchant can submit transactions on chain and generate ed25519 sigs quickly

backend_referrer:
This is just a signature generator and will send click metrics to off chain server.
This can be offloaded to my servers if they want

frontend_merchant:
This is some frontend code that interacts with the users browser extension

frontend_referrer:
this is the code for if the referrer wants to host their own frontend software
This can be offloaded to my servers if they want

frontend_user:
this is the browser extension for the user

